Feature: Customers
 
Scenario: Search customer by FirstName
 Given User Launch Chrome browser
 And user opens URL "https://admin-demo.nopcommerce.com/login"
 And user enters Email as "admin@yourstore.com" and password as "admin"
 When user click on Login
 Then user can view Dashboard
 When user click on Customers Menu
 And click on customers Menu Item
 And user landed on Customers Page
 And user entered firstname as "a" in FirstName field
 When user click on Search button
 Then search results related to FirstName "a" will be displayed
 And close browser
 
 
 